version_description:
It says only the smart cannot be fooled on April Fools' Day, so are you ready for this? We've also updated new exciting Easter event!

Update:
- 1 new room
- 73 new levels

The kittens are so lovely, and I feel so touched when they act like a spoiled child before me. The Father's Day is coming. We have prepared some new outfit for the kittens, and hope you and your kittens like them!

Updates:
- 7-day benefits for beginners
- Optimization of the story of the first 3 rooms
- New outfit for the Father's Day
- New icon of the game
- Adjustment of the difficulty of new levels
- Optimization of items
- One new room
